7ba1","tid":589912,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"五毛狗要反擊了。"},{"pid":"b2391d3417e20bbae44af406f18a3635ac4f281f","tid":589912,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"想問下泛民唔係應該4席全取咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/589143/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/589143/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"24bc7ae2c20eb842f2e818589a68d8e9d75f9118","tid":589912,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"有11萬粉絲的Twitter用戶@jbkk988（Peter Kong）在網上發文指，廣東廣州的公共交通工具、行人路上都出現用繁體書寫「廣州獨立 香港加油」的字樣，在不同地方出現的字句字體相似，疑是同一個人所為。<br />\n<br />\nPeter Kong發文指，「香港去年出現『港獨』字眼的橫額及海報後，連廣州（也）出現「廣獨」標句，獨立風潮蔓延中國內地！」。從他發出的照片可見，在巴士椅背、巴士站上都可見到用雙頭筆寫上的「廣州獨立 香港加油」，「『廣獨』的標句，遍布（佈）交通工具及行人路，包括出現於大元帥府巴士站、新鴻花園巴士站、以及多個巴士坐位的椅背上，即使行人石屎路上亦被寫上標句」；他並說「港獨向粵獨致敬，港獨是粵獨天然盟友」。"},{"pid":"6285c0755ced2f89520fc8701d34d11d6ef76352","tid":589912,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180312/photo/bkn-20180312111957470-0312_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180312131746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180312%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180312111957470-0312_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180312131746&h=b25b2a19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8de71bbadbc08d9b3e1fb509438b57f98acc3271","tid":589912,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2391d3417e20bbae44af406f18a3635ac4f281f","tid":589912,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"想問下泛民唔係應該4席全取咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/589143/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/589143/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"以未來人報告為準。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerfac